Source Directory: All code resides in frontend/src.
Core Directories: Adhere strictly to this structure:
src/assets: Images, fonts.
src/components: Reusable UI components.
common/: Atomic components (Button, Input).
layout/: Structural components (Header, Container).
src/hooks: Custom React hooks (useCamelCase.ts).
src/navigation: All React Navigation setup.
src/screens: Top-level screen components.
src/services: API call logic.
src/store: Global state (Zustand/Redux).
src/theme: Centralized theme and styling values.
src/types: Global TypeScript definitions.

src/utils: Helper functions.